{"tid":1817992,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"​廣東確診一宗外地傳入寨卡病毒感染個案","createTime":"2020-01-09T13:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T14:05:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"df597265f46389247ffc0dc1f33c0d8fdb108a3a","tid":1817992,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心接獲廣東省衞生健康委員會通報，​廣東確診一宗外地傳入寨卡病毒感染個案，呼籲市民外遊期間時刻採取防蚊措施，孕婦不應前往受影響地區。<br />\n<br />\n中心表示，這名​31歲男病人本月6日​從柬埔寨​返抵深圳寶安國際機場，入境時被發現發燒。個案之後確診，病人情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n中心發言人說，所有口岸的恆常健康監測一直為入境旅客監測體溫。但由於大部分受感染病人沒有出現病徵，呼籲任何人從寨卡受影響地區到港後至少21日內須繼續使用昆蟲驅避劑，減低傳播風險。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501942-20200109.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501942-20200109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF06crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=f2933346\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501942-20200109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=272d4241\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501942-20200109.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"56cf461c8ad28e9cc637dbc1bd17c38fcaca4067","tid":1817992,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【大和解】退場風波搞到連登少左好多人, 幫手推呢個POST比多啲勇武睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817975</a>"},{"pid":"12d9d68181a7557c39c81b4612c51b6c33835c8d","tid":1817992,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"支那 發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bfea5afa849325823f207309317db6b2fa23bc","tid":1817992,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets